            "bucket": "vocabulary.it.lavare.translation"
          }
        }
      }
    ],
    "explanation": "'L'ho lavata ieri' means 'I washed it yesterday'. La macchina is f.sg → DOP la, which elides to l' before ho. The participle 'lavata' in the prompt is the participle agreement triggered by the preceding f.sg DOP. Stack: la + ho + lavata giving 'l'ho lavata'.",
    "examiner_note": "Accepts 'l'' or 'la'. The elision bucket is tested separately in op_dop_elide_*.",
