    "explanation": "'Signor Rossi, Le ho mandato il documento ieri' means 'Mr Rossi, I sent you the document yesterday'. Mandare qualcosa a qualcuno opens an indirect-object slot for the addressee. In formal address that's the IOP Le. The DOP La would be the wrong role (e.g. 'La saluto' = 'I greet you').",
    "examiner_note": "Diagnostic between formal La (DOP) and formal Le (IOP). The verb's argument structure resolves it.",
    "version": 1
  },
  {
    "external_id": "op_iop_verbs_iop_01",
