          }
        }
      }
    ],
    "explanation": "'Me lo dai?' means 'Will you give it to me?'. In an Italian clitic cluster the IOP comes first, then the DOP. Il libro is m.sg → DOP lo. Stack: me + lo giving 'me lo dai'.",
    "examiner_note": "Tests order specifically, given the vowel change is already shown.",
    "version": 1
  },
  {
    "external_id": "op_comb_order_02",
