    "explanation": "'Hai dato i fiori ad Anna? Sì, glieli ho dati' means 'Did you give the flowers to Anna? Yes, I gave them to her'. Two rules combine. The feminine IOP le shifts to glie- in the glielo-family transform, just like the masculine gli. I fiori is m.pl → DOP li. Stack: le + li → glieli. The IOP's gender (feminine, Anna) is invisible in the cluster.",
