          }
        }
      }
    ],
    "explanation": "'Hai visto le foto della festa? Sì, ne ho viste solo alcune' means 'Have you seen the party photos? Yes, I've only seen some of them'. Two rules combine. The quantifier alcune signals the partitive, so the partitive ne is required (the DOP le would mean 'all of them'). Participle agreement gives viste (f.pl, matching foto).",
    "examiner_note": "Hot spot. The 'le ho viste' option is the more common error (using DOP instead of partitive ne); 'ne ho visto' is the over-extension of m.sg default to ne contexts.",
    "version": 1
  },
