          }
        }
      }
    ],
    "explanation": "'Riesci ad arrivare in tempo? No, non ci riesco mai' means 'Can you manage to arrive on time? No, I never manage it'. Riuscire A + infinitive means 'to manage to'. The locative ci stands in for the whole a-complement. 'Non ci riesco' = 'I can't manage it'.",
    "version": 1
  },
