    "vocab_help": [],
    "explanation": "'vederlo' = 'to see him/it'. On an infinitive the clitic takes the attached position: the infinitive drops its final -e and the clitic joins as one word. Stack: vedere → veder-, then + lo, giving vederlo.",
    "version": 1
  },
  {
