          }
        }
      }
    ],
    "explanation": "'Lo voglio vedere' means 'I want to see it'. With a modal verb plus an infinitive, the clitic has two valid positions: pre-verb before the modal ('lo voglio vedere') or attached to the infinitive ('voglio vederlo'). Both are standard. Putting the clitic between modal and infinitive is forbidden.",
