            "bucket": "vocabulary.it.stanco.translation"
          }
        }
      }
    ],
    "explanation": "'Sei stanca? Sì, lo sono' means 'Are you tired? Yes, I am'. Neuter lo can resume a predicate, here the adjective stanca. The lo stays invariable: it doesn't agree with the gender of the original adjective.",
    "examiner_note": "Diagnostic: not 'la sono' (using fem agreement), not 'sono stanca' (no resumption). The neuter lo is invariant.",
    "version": 1
  },
