    "explanation": "'Pensi che pioverà? Sì, lo penso' means 'Do you think it will rain? Yes, I think so'. When the antecedent is a clause (here 'che pioverà'), the resuming pronoun is neuter lo. 'Lo penso' means 'I think so'.",
    "examiner_note": "Diagnostic against 'ci penso' (which would only work if the antecedent were an a-phrase or topic) and 'ne penso' (which needs an opinion-of complement).",
