    "vocab_help": [],
    "explanation": "'Hai visto le ragazze? Sì, le ho viste al bar' means 'Have you seen the girls? Yes, I saw them at the bar'. The plural DOP le does NOT undergo elision. The participle 'viste' confirms the f.pl antecedent; mixing singular elision with plural agreement isn't used.",
    "version": 1
  },
  {
