    "explanation": "'Me ne sto a casa stasera' means 'I'm staying in tonight'. Starsene is a pronominal idiomatic verb: stare with lexicalised reflexive + ne, meaning 'to keep oneself somewhere'. The ne doesn't refer to anything; it just belongs to the verb. 1sg: mi shifts to me before ne. Stack: me + ne + sto.",
