    "explanation": "'Hai abbastanza tempo per finire? Sì, ne ho abbastanza' means 'Do you have enough time to finish? Yes, I have enough of it'. Quantifier abbastanza + dropped noun (tempo) → partitive ne. Not ci (ci would replace an a-phrase or location).",
