    "vocab_help": [],
    "explanation": "'Buongiorno dottore, La informiamo che la Sua richiesta è stata accettata' means 'Good morning Doctor, we inform you that your request has been accepted'. Business correspondence is the prototypical capitalisation context for formal address. Both the formal pronouns and the formal possessives take a capital.",
    "version": 1
  },
